{
  "stem": "13213.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And a speaker came from-- I think [INAUDIBLE] and some others-- a big hall in Paris, and I went to listen to him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And I got all excited, and I registered to go to Israel, to fight for Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "About three days later, I was shipped-- went to Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And from Marseilles, we were on the boat [INAUDIBLE], which was already an Israeli boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And with [INAUDIBLE], we arrived to Haifa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "That was already the end of '48.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "I think the station was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "In [INAUDIBLE], I-- we stayed about maybe three days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And that was the time after the Latrun fighting, where Israel lost a lot of soldiers near Jerusalem-- Latrun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "The Seventh Brigade of the Palmach, and [INAUDIBLE] came to recruit some more young men to fill in the unit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And he picked me and some other guys to go to the Palmach, into unit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And the next day, we were shipped to Beersheba.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And we had training for a couple days, and went on the Jordanian front near Beersheba, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "The front line was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "That was Passover of 1949.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "I remember Passover because we didn't get any matzohs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "The Jordanians cut off the road that led our supplies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "And then, our soldiers came and they opened up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And one of my friends was killed in [INAUDIBLE] while we were on a mission.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "I felt very good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "I felt excited about it, because finally, I am a free man and I fight for my own country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And I had nobody else, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "I didn't know what happened to my brothers [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
